<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.7.1/dist/leaflet.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">
        <title>NestMart - Home Suppliers</title>
    </head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light fixed-top">
            <h1 class="navbar-brand"><a href="/">NestMart</a></h1>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item <%= page === 'home' ? 'active' : '' %>"><a class="nav-link" href="/">HOME</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item <%= page === 'products' ? 'active' : '' %>"><a class="nav-link" href="/products">Products</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item <%= page === 'orders' ? 'active' : '' %>"><a class="nav-link" href="/orders">Your Orders</a></li>
                    <% if (user && user.isAdmin) { %>
                        <li class="nav-item <%= page === 'admin' ? 'active' : '' %>"><a class="nav-link" href="/admin">Admin</a></li>
                    <% } else if (user) { %>
                        <li class="nav-item <%= page === 'profile' ? 'active' : '' %>"><a class="nav-link" href="/profile">Profile</a></li>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <li class="nav-item <%= page === 'login' ? 'active' : '' %>"><a class="nav-link" href="/login">Log in</a></li>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                    <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                    <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                    <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                </ol>
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="/img/hom1.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>Find Everything for Your Home</h5>
                        <p>Explore our top-quality home supplies. Reliable, affordable, and delivered to your doorstep.</p>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/img/hom2.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>Expert Tips for Your Home</h5>
                        <p>Discover guides and tutorials on choosing the best home supplies. Tips from industry experts.</p>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="/img/hom3.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>Exclusive Deals on Home Essentials</h5>
                        <p>Don't miss out on discounts and promotions on top-quality home supplies. Comfort and quality at the best prices.</p>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                </a>
                <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button" data-slide="next">
                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                </a>
            </div>
            <section class="welcome my-5">
                <h2>Welcome to NestMart</h2>
                <p><strong id="greeting"></strong><strong> Welcome to NestMart — your one-stop shop for quality home supplies and essentials.</strong>
                    At NestMart, we believe that a well-equipped home creates a comfortable and efficient lifestyle. We are here to provide you with a wide range of top-quality home products, from everyday necessities to unique finds that enhance your living space. Our mission goes beyond just selling products — we offer practical solutions to make your home more functional and stylish.  
                    Our carefully curated selection includes high-quality home essentials, kitchenware, cleaning supplies, and more, sourced from trusted brands and innovative suppliers. Each item is chosen to bring convenience, durability, and value to your home.  
                    In addition to our products, we provide expert tips and guides to help you make informed choices and maintain a well-organized home. Whether you need storage solutions, home improvement ideas, or eco-friendly alternatives, NestMart is here to assist you every step of the way.  
                </p>
            
                <dl>
                    <p>At NestMart, we are committed to making home shopping simple, affordable, and enjoyable. Discover everything you need for a cozy and well-equipped home — all in one place.</p>
                </dl>
            </section>

            <section id="weather" class="my-5">
                <h2>Current Weather in Astana</h2>
                <p>Temperature: <span id="temperature"></span> °C</p>
                <p>Description: <span id="description"></span></p>
                <p>Icon: <img id="icon" class="weather-icon" src="" alt="Weather icon"></p>
                <p>Coordinates: <span id="coordinates"></span></p>
                <p>Feels Like: <span id="feels-like"></span> °C</p>
                <p>Humidity: <span id="humidity"></span> %</p>
                <p>Pressure: <span id="pressure"></span> hPa</p>
                <p>Wind Speed: <span id="wind-speed"></span> m/s</p>
                <p>Country Code: <span id="country-code"></span></p>
                <p>Rain Volume (last 3 hours): <span id="rain-volume"></span> mm</p>
            </section>
            
            <section class="motivational my-5 text-center">
                <h2>Transform Your Home, Transform Your Life</h2>
                <p>"A home is not a place, it's a feeling." - Charles Dickens</p>
                <p>At NestMart, we believe that a well-equipped home brings comfort, peace, and joy. Our curated selection of quality home supplies and essentials is designed to help you create a space that reflects your unique style and enhances your daily life.</p>
            </section>
            
            <section id="map" class="my-5" style="height: 500px;">
                <h2>Map Location</h2>
                <div id="mapid" style="height: 100%;"></div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="products my-5">
                <h2>Our Top Products</h2>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="card">
                            <img src="/img/fridge.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Product 1">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">The Samsung Fridge RB31FERNDSA</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">The Samsung RB31FERNDSA offers a spacious 339L capacity with a No Frost system to keep your food fresh without the hassle of manual defrosting. Equipped with an energy-efficient design, it includes a Multi-Airflow cooling system for even temperature distribution and quieter operation at 37 dB. Perfect for any modern kitchen.</p>
                                <p><strong>$499.99</strong></p>
                                <a href="/product-detail/2" class="btn btn-primary">View Details</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="card">
                            <img src="/img/vac.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Robot Vacuum Tefal RG7447WH Explorer Serie 60 White">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">Robot Vacuum Tefal RG7447WH Explorer Serie 60 White</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">The Tefal RG7447WH Explorer Serie 60 is a sleek, powerful robot vacuum designed for efficient cleaning with advanced navigation. It features multiple cleaning modes, including spot cleaning and edge cleaning, with a long-lasting battery for extended cleaning sessions.</p>
                                <p><strong>$499.99</strong></p>
                                <a href="/product-detail/2" class="btn btn-primary">View Details</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                        <div class="card">
                            <img src="/img/hai.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Haier Washing Machine HW60-BP12919B">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">Haier Washing Machine HW60-BP12919B</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">The Haier HW60-BP12919B is a compact 6kg front-loading washing machine with a 1000 RPM spin speed for efficient cleaning and water extraction. It offers a range of wash programs, ensuring that your laundry needs are met, while maintaining energy efficiency and quiet operation at 72 dB.</p>
                                <p><strong>$299.99</strong></p>
                                <a href="/product-detail/3" class="btn btn-primary">View Details</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>

        <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.5.4/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.7.1/dist/leaflet.js"></script>
        <script src="/js/home.js"></script>
        <p style="text-align: center;">&copy; Ali Ainur, Akerke Kassymbekova IT-2308</p>
        <script>
            function clearProduct(id) {
                fetch(`/clear-product/${id}`, {
                    method: 'POST'
                })
                .then(response => {
                    if (response.ok) {
                        location.reload();
                    } else {
                        console.error('Error clearing product');
                    }
                });
            }
        </script>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
